snippet.title: The Most Stupid Trailer You Will Watch in 2023
snippet.description:
We made a stupid trailer for our indie game. We hope you will still buy it. If you do, you're officially a super cool person.

Wishlist Super Kill-BOI 9000 now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2126400/Super_KillBOI_9000/

It will be released April 27th, 2023 @ 08:00 AM PT | 05:00 PM CET
You can also play the demo in the browser: https://playwithfurcifer.itch.io/kill-boi-9000
